<h2 id="in-closing">In Closing</h2>
<p>Setting up InfluxDB is super simple (albeit there are a few steps to follow) and should take you no longer than 10 min if following this guide.</p>
<p>InfluxDB is an awesome time-series database and performs fast even on the oldest hardware \ single board computers, and when paired with <a href="https://grafana.com/">Grafana</a> makes an awesome addition to my home automation monitoring.</p>
